body: Tarps with boobies are so hot

Ok finished, and I'd rank them like this, Binto > the last artist > Hanamaki Kaeru > Palco Nagashima > Hayashida Toranosuke > 2nd to the last artist, Binto's part really killed it this time the detailed ass holes, the wonderful sex positions and damn lovely facial expressions, both Nagashima and Kaeru have equal and standard quality but not really that good they suffer from being repetitive, and man the last artist has potential I hope for more works from him in the future, as for the others they're pretty meh...not bad but nor that good the 2nd to the last artist has some hiccups with the art here and there but kinda shows quality at some pages, Toranosuke's part is nice but really kinda falls flat at some points, so yeah I'll give this a 7/10 pretty nice despite some shortcomings, also I bet once Binto's part gets translated a lot people will quickly smash the favorite button until it reaches 3000+ favorites like what happened to Nii-chan wa Bitch Gyaru.
